Bias &quot;The Power of Independent Trucking&quot; Schmias <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uaxterixenobelix.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Axterix EnObelix</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Standard</span><br>  Posts: 23<br> <font color=#FFFF00>(3/12/01 8:50:53 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ftherathetravelagencyfrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=80.topic&index=20>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Verant</span><hr size=1> &gt;&gt;Verant does not AGREE with your calender system nor will they enforce it. According to verant they cannot enforce it but they can punish those who try and claim and entire zone. (this isn't a threat by the way....it is a fact). I have spoken to verant on this issue on several occassions and have posted their comments. They will not now nor will they ever enforce your calender system. <br>
